               <p>NEW COURT. THURSDAY, SEPTEMBER 23.</p>
               <p>Third Middlesex Jury. - Before Mr. Common Sergeant.</p>
               <p>1796. 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-313-defend2568" type="defendantName">
                     JOHN 
                     SMITH
                  <interp inst="t18300916-313-defend2568" type="surname" value="SMITH"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-defend2568" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>
