                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-defend2568" type="age" value="15"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             and 
               
                  <persName id="t18300916-313-defend2570" type="defendantName">
                     WILLIAM 
                     HALL
                  <interp inst="t18300916-313-defend2570" type="surname" value="HALL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-defend2570" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-defend2570" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-defend2570" type="age" value="17"></interp>
                  </persName>
               
             were indicted for <rs id="t18300916-313-off1605" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-off1605" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-off1605" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18300916-313-cd1606" type="crimeDate">16th of September</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-313-off1605 t18300916-313-cd1606"></join>, I handkerchief, value 4s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18300916-313-victim2572" type="victimName">
                           David 
                           Lewis
                        <interp inst="t18300916-313-victim2572" type="surname" value="Lewis"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18300916-313-victim2572" type="given" value="David"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18300916-313-victim2572" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-313-off1605 t18300916-313-victim2572"></join>
                     </persName>
                     
                  , from his person
            </rs>.</p>

               <p>DAVID LEWIS. I am a <rs id="t18300916-313-viclabel1607" type="occupation">medical man</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-313-victim2572 t18300916-313-viclabel1607"></join>. On the 16th of September, as I was in <placeName id="t18300916-313-crimeloc1608">St. John's-square, Clerkenwell</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18300916-313-crimeloc1608" type="placeName" value="St. John's-square, Clerkenwell"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18300916-313-crimeloc1608" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18300916-313-off1605 t18300916-313-crimeloc1608"></join>, I felt something pull at my pocket; I turned and saw Smith putting my handkerchief into Hall's bosom - I had had it half a minute before; I seized Hall, and Smith ran away - I called Stop thief! he was brought back in about a minute; I had lost sight of him, but I am sure he is the person.</p>
               <p>Hall. Q. Can you swear I was with Smith? A. Yes; the handkerchief was put into your bosom - I seized you, and took it from you - you wanted me to let you go, and said you knew nothing about it.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-313-person2573">
                  CHARLES 
                  DENNIS
               <interp inst="t18300916-313-person2573" type="surname" value="DENNIS"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-person2573" type="given" value="CHARLES"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-person2573" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I was coming through Jerusalem-passage, and saw the two prisoners walking just a-head of me; Mr. Lewis was walking with two others - when he got to a broad part, Smith took the handkerchief, and put it into Hall's bosom; Lewis seized Hall - Smith ran off; I pursued, cried Stop thief! and he was stopped without getting out of my sight - I had seen them together for one hundred yards.</p>
               <p>Hall. Q. Can you say I was with Smith? A. Yes, and when I came up to you, you said, "You did not see me take the handkerchief."</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18300916-313-person2574">
                  WILLIAM 
                  HILL
               <interp inst="t18300916-313-person2574" type="surname" value="HILL"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-person2574" type="given" value="WILLIAM"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-person2574" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I stopped Smith, who was coming towards me.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Hall's Defence. it was thrown at me, it lodged between my coat and waistcoat; I know nothing of Smith.</p>

               <p>SMITH - <rs id="t18300916-313-verdict1609" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-verdict1609" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 15.</p>
               <p>HALL - <rs id="t18300916-313-verdict1610" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18300916-313-verdict1610" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 17.</p>
